{"tid":740110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【調查】港女愛嘅上進心即係咩？交友配對公司咁解釋","createTime":"2018-07-12T15:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T12:52:50.000Z","uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"df264f8e82441c1967030644e8e38ccbbfb6693e","tid":740110,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"又再次證明港女口中既上進心=錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔信有條友有幾千萬,但做廢青<br />\n班港雞會唔要<br />\n要個日日勤力返工,但得兩萬既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交友配對公司HK Romance Dating調查發現，61%港女認為異性擁有私樓最為吸引，不過創辦人張惠萍補充「有物業唔上進都係死症」，「(港女)唔係有樓就兩眼發光，乜都唔理。」<br />\n<br />\n張解釋，港女選擇交往時，有沒有物業都未必是首要條件，「最緊要有人生規劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">好似熱愛自己事業，不斷晉升；又或者有兼職、小生意搵錢</span>，會畀到女仔安全感。」此外儲錢能力亦是考慮因素，願為組織家庭儲一定比例金錢，相較「搵五萬，但九成使晒」會更為吸引。<br />\n張又以遇過的個案為例，一個有樓office boy，「女仔會問，男仔有無打算讀多啲書？會唔會轉去其他部門，學多啲嘢？」不過office boy認為現況很好，工作冇壓力，不必帶工作回家，張稱「就算佢有物業，女仔考慮佢嘅機會都係低。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180712/58432756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432756&d=aWL1b99BwFmFs2mBFk4Flhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2774125d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432756&h=ca984c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180712/58432756</a>"},{"pid":"9489e451b0b4c491c0fa2136400828f709713c44","tid":740110,"uid":58257,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"首先你要有錢，然後你要搵到更加多既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3a81864ca4dd91840ca721218767c166f3deb5","tid":740110,"uid":25618,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"df264f8e82441c1967030644