c=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交友配對公司HK Romance Dating調查發現，61%港女認為異性擁有私樓最為吸引，不過創辦人張惠萍補充「有物業唔上進都係死症」，「(港女)唔係有樓就兩眼發光，乜都唔理。」<br />\n<br />\n張解釋，港女選擇交往時，有沒有物業都未必是首要條件，「最緊要有人生規劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">好似熱愛自己事業，不斷晉升；又或者有兼職、小生意搵錢</span>，會畀到女仔安全感。」此外儲錢能力亦是考慮因素，願為組織家庭儲一定比例金錢，相較「搵五萬，但九成使晒」會更為吸引。<br />\n張又以遇過的個案為例，一個有樓office boy，「女仔會問，男仔有無打算讀多啲書？會唔會轉去其他部門，學多啲嘢？」不過office boy認為現況很好，工作冇壓力，不必帶工作回家，張稱「就算佢有物業，女仔考慮佢嘅機會都係低。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180712/58432756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432756&d=aWL1b99BwFmFs2mBFk4Flhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2774125d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432756&h=ca984c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180712/58432756</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會呀 ? 我覺得有樓既office boy , 好過揾三四萬既專業人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬有樓收租,passive income已經差好遠"},{"pid":"be724da18b9e6e606aa820a8ed1f65b15bc951a2","tid":740110,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d7e922d47a796faa1a2ce716495a86738b493ea","tid":740110,"uid":13914,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"好似熱愛自己事業，不斷晉升；又或者有兼職、小生意搵錢<br />\n<br />\n同時應該加上不能影響或減少二人相處時間, 男方應該隨傳隨到, 因返工ot失約者out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo